.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, skiing
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, teacher
3 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, trike
1. the teacher is the person driving the bus##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is the person driving the trike##1
6. the teacher is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Sport       | skiing | swimming    | weightlifting |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | mouse     | frog        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

