.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, reading
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, pony
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, blue, ebony
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | reading   | photography | fishing  |
| Pet         | pony      | lizard      | ferret   |
| Color       | blue      | ebony       | green |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike       | tram     |

