.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, water
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, canadian
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, grey
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, volleyball
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the australian is the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes grey is between the canadian and the australian##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | water    | lemonade   | fanta      |
| Nationality   | canadian | american   | australian |
| Color           | ivory      | grey      | lilac      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | rugby      |

