The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, punk, rock
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | cola    | lemonade | mirinda  |
| Hobby         | singing | writing  | reading  |
| Game   | domino | canasta     | backgammon |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | rock     | punk     |

