.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, mirinda
City: hamburg, liverpool, paris
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the bike##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | fanta        | mirinda |
| City   | hamburg | liverpool | paris  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Transport     | bike      | snowmobile   | ship    |

